from all the parsings i have seen and my own testing, it looks like there is a 2% chance of innate crit.  When you crit it will do anywhere from 1% to 66% extra damage.  Its basically a ghetto version of casting fury 2 with a 2% chance instead of 4%.  still pretty cool, goes off often if you are quad kiting (8% chance per AoE)
