<HR size="1" color="#dedfdf">
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Innate crits appear to stack with AA crits; the AA rolls are made separately to the innate rolls.<P>With Casting Fury 1 your chance to crit was 2%. As I understand it, it is now ~4%<P>You also have a massive 0.04% chance of a "double crit". One every 2500 nukes, or once every 32 hours in a single-target group, according to my rough squint at my personal figures. Working backwards, that puts my innate crits at once every ~40 minutes in an exp group.
</FONT>
