quiring far more time and to get back up to snuff than a mage re-summoning his pet.<BR>5 &#8211; Pet hit for 70 &#8211; Stop making things up. This is simply false.<BR>6 &#8211; Buffed to have 500 more HP &#8211; Again, get a HP buff for your pet and shut up.<BR>7 &#8211; 150pt DD proc that&#8217;s unresistable &#8211; Again, false. Stop making things up.<BR> <BLOCKQUOTE><font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">quote:</font><HR> Conclusion: <HR></BLOCKQUOTE><BR>Show yourself some respect and shut up before your non-existent arguments and made-up facts make you appear even more pathetic and petulant than you already do. If you really had the gall to send this to Verant, you can rest assured that they had a good chuckle at your expense before disregarding it.<P>/rant off<P>--------------------<P>Balance doesn&#8217;t always mean you getting more and/or others getting less. Sometimes you have to recognize that you should be the one to not get more, or to give something up.
